          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原故。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，住轿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "青袍甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老爷撤料。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你们前去问那妇人：因何在此哭哭啼啼？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（青袍甲允。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "青袍",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那一妇人：因何在此哭哭啼啼？"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "萧素贞这里把头抬，"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "尊一声老爷你哪里来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "京中来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "坟前里没有关王庙，"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "坟后里没有接官亭。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "坟西里没有陷马坑。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你为何到我刘家的新坟？"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "坟东里没有放马场"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "又不通南北共大道，我的爷吓"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，你们对那妇人言道：说你老爷是清官到了，有何冤枉，叫她亲口诉来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（青袍甲允。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "青袍甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那一妇人：我家老爷是清官到了，有何冤枉，亲口诉来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听说一声清官到，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你这妇人，有何冤枉，一一诉来。有你老爷与你作主。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "容禀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "青袍",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老爷吃饼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我有心状告无人写，"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "口诉的状词句句真。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "告的是公婆二双亲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打骂着奴家实实的难忍。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "头一状不把别人告"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "终日里打来每日里骂，我的爷吓"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "世间哪有不是的公婆？公婆打骂，古之常理。头状不准，二状诉来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "容禀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "青袍甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老爷吃粽子。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "第二状不把别人告，"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "告的是娘舅李大公。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "挑唆我公婆二双亲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打骂着奴家逼我改嫁人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他每日三次我家走"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "终日里打来每日里骂"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "世间之上，哪有这等公婆。我却不准，三状诉来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三状我就不告了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，你去对那妇人言道：说你老爷准了状了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（青袍甲允。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "青袍甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那一妇人：我家老爷准了状了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么着，你老爷准了我的状了？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（青袍甲允。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此还要告。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三状不把别人告，"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "告的是儿夫刘禄敬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "二青袍",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唗！"
        },
        {
          "character": "青袍甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "提老爷杂讳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "下去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "青袍甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要伺候老爷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "没有你们的事。赏你两张军用钞票，到兰芳里去把老虫跳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "青袍甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老爷回府，还是乘轿、骑马？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "全不用，我有黄包车，下去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二青袍同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我的爷吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "上写着儿夫命丧东京城。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "上三年有封家书到"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为官这里怒气冲，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "骂一声娘舅李大公："
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三百两银子书一封。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你不该说我命丧东京城。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先斩我娘舅李大公。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "认认你亲夫刘禄敬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我在京中恩待你"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "埋没了我银子是小事"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "圣上赐我上方剑"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫一声贤妻你认一认"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "指望你是清官到，"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来你是个糊涂虫。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人皮包着畜类精。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "少鞍无髻你也认不成。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是我亲夫转家门；"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你就公子王孙，你也认不成。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "公案之下伸双手"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "槽头挽着逍遥马"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你若对得上三桩宝"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你若对不上三桩宝"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤妻打我我不恼，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤妻骂我我不嗔。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "桩桩件件记得清。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫一声贤妻你来认分明。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将她当做裙钗女"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宝贝放在尘埃地"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "拿起乌绫看一看，"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四四方方好乌绫。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "八月十五放光明。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "千针万线我做成。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "禄敬还是假禄敬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "拿起梨花照一照"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "拿起花鞋对一对"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，宝贝乃是真宝贝"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宝贝本是真宝贝，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "禄敬本是真禄敬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我亲夫上京去，"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "乃是十七、八岁的念书人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "满脸上长胡须好不愁人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到如今，你回来"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "上京时，我的妻，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "年方二八的女裙钗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "满脸的长皱纹好不丑人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到如今，我回来"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有皱纹，无皱纹，与你何干？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有胡须，无胡须，与你何论？"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既是我的亲夫到，"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还有几桩大事情："
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪里庄上有家门？"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兄弟同胞有几人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妻子叫得甚芳名？"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "家住哪州并哪县"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爹姓甚来娘姓甚"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "娶的妻子谁家女"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "家住山东即墨县。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刘家庄上有家门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "母亲吃斋行善人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只有我禄敬一个人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "她的名字叫素贞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爹爹就是刘员外"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "上无兄来下无弟"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "娶的妻子萧家女"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听说是我亲夫到，"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴家随你到接官亭。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为官的这里头里走，"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "后面随着萧素贞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忙将乌纱整一整，"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "头上摘下孝白绫。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只说是夫妻难相认，"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日相逢在接官亭。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "回去吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘禄敬、萧素贞同哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "娘子，你我分别多年，你在家中，何人照应于你？"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我来看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧素贞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，正厅上洋装打扮，戴金丝眼镜的，小白脸儿，照应我的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘禄敬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "承蒙照应。明天请你坐汽车，吃大餐。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘禄敬、萧素贞同下。）"
        }
      ],
